Subject: drm/amdgpu: switch from 'pci_' to 'dma_' API
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 8a1d1bdb845affbb2a9887826e5e991e290bde56
